            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Standard time of flight technique. The scattering",
                "sphere was placed 60 mm from the target and the",
                "detector about 210 mm from the scatterer in 105 deg."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two methods were used for monitoring of the",
                "incident neutron flux, viz. beam current integration",
                "and a LiI-polythene counter, the latter being placed",
                "well within the cone of neutron emission to avoid undue",
                "dependence on fluctuations of the proton energy, and",
                "further at a position such as to eliminate any possible",
                "interference from scattering."
              ]
